45GElf_Cap *
46gelf_getcap(Elf_Data *ed, int ndx, GElf_Cap *dst)
47{
48 int ec;
49 Elf *e;
50 size_t msz;
51 Elf_Scn *scn;
52 Elf32_Cap *cap32;
53 Elf64_Cap *cap64;
54 uint32_t sh_type;
55 struct _Libelf_Data *d;
56
57 d = (struct _Libelf_Data *) ed;
58
59 if (d == NULL || ndx < 0 || dst == NULL ||
60 (scn = d->d_scn) == NULL ||
61 (e = scn->s_elf) == NULL) {
62 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARGUMENT, 0);
63 return (NULL);
64 }
65
66 ec = e->e_class;
67 assert(ec == ELFCLASS32 || ec == ELFCLASS64);
68
69 if (ec == ELFCLASS32)
70 sh_type = scn->s_shdr.s_shdr32.sh_type;
71 else
72 sh_type = scn->s_shdr.s_shdr64.sh_type;
73
74 if (_libelf_xlate_shtype(sh_type) != ELF_T_CAP) {
75 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARGUMENT, 0);
76 return (NULL);
77 }
78
79 msz = _libelf_msize(ELF_T_CAP, ec, e->e_version);
80
81 assert(msz > 0);
82
83 if (msz * (size_t) ndx >= d->d_data.d_size) {
84 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARGUMENT, 0);
85 return (NULL);
86 }
87
88 if (ec == ELFCLASS32) {
89
90 cap32 = (Elf32_Cap *) d->d_data.d_buf + ndx;
91
92 dst->c_tag = cap32->c_tag;
93 dst->c_un.c_val = (Elf64_Xword) cap32->c_un.c_val;
94
95 } else {
96
97 cap64 = (Elf64_Cap *) d->d_data.d_buf + ndx;
98
99 *dst = *cap64;
100 }
101
102 return (dst);
103}
104
105int
106gelf_update_cap(Elf_Data *ed, int ndx, GElf_Cap *gc)
107{
108 int ec;
109 Elf *e;
110 size_t msz;
111 Elf_Scn *scn;
112 Elf32_Cap *cap32;
113 Elf64_Cap *cap64;
114 uint32_t sh_type;
115 struct _Libelf_Data *d;
116
117 d = (struct _Libelf_Data *) ed;
118
119 if (d == NULL || ndx < 0 || gc == NULL ||
120 (scn = d->d_scn) == NULL ||
121 (e = scn->s_elf) == NULL) {
122 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARGUMENT, 0);
123 return (0);
124 }
125
126 ec = e->e_class;
127 assert(ec == ELFCLASS32 || ec == ELFCLASS64);
128
129 if (ec == ELFCLASS32)
130 sh_type = scn->s_shdr.s_shdr32.sh_type;
131 else
132 sh_type = scn->s_shdr.s_shdr64.sh_type;
133
134 if (_libelf_xlate_shtype(sh_type) != ELF_T_CAP) {
135 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARGUMENT, 0);
136 return (0);
137 }
138
139 msz = _libelf_msize(ELF_T_CAP, ec, e->e_version);
140 assert(msz > 0);
141
142 if (msz * (size_t) ndx >= d->d_data.d_size) {
143 LIBELF_SET_ERROR(ARGUMENT, 0);
144 return (0);
145 }
146
147 if (ec == ELFCLASS32) {
148 cap32 = (Elf32_Cap *) d->d_data.d_buf + ndx;
149
150 LIBELF_COPY_U32(cap32, gc, c_tag);
151 LIBELF_COPY_U32(cap32, gc, c_un.c_val);
152 } else {
153 cap64 = (Elf64_Cap *) d->d_data.d_buf + ndx;
154
155 *cap64 = *gc;
156 }
157
158 return (1);
159}
